ATTRIBUTION AND INSPIRATION

Portions of this project—including the name GLX and aspects of its civic 
networking concept—are inspired by the fictional app depicted in Gatchaman 
Crowds (© Tatsunoko Production). This project has no official connection to 
Tatsunoko Production or the anime series.

The GLX name and civic networking liquid democracy concepts were inspired 
by the fictional GLX app portrayed in the Gatchaman Crowds anime series, 
which is the intellectual property of Tatsunoko Production.

All source code is licensed under the PolyForm Shield License 1.0.0 unless 
otherwise noted.

